4707 void LineQuadrature::get_quadrature(const int order, Quadrature &quad)
4708 {
4709 std::vector<double> xi = quadrature_points(order);
4710 std::vector<double> wi = quadrature_weights(order);
4711
4712 assert((xi.size() == wi.size()));
4713
4714 std::sort(wi.begin(), wi.end(), [xi](int i1, int i2) {
4715 return xi[i1] < xi[i2];
4716 });
4717
4718 std::sort(xi.begin(), xi.end(), [xi](int i1, int i2) {
4719 return xi[i1] < xi[i2];
4720 });
4721
4722 quad.points = Eigen::Map<Eigen::MatrixXd>(&xi[0], xi.size(), 1);
4723 quad.weights = Eigen::Map<Eigen::MatrixXd>(&wi[0], wi.size(), 1);
4724
4725 quad.weights /= 2;
4726 quad.points /= 2;
4727 quad.points += Eigen::MatrixXd::Ones(quad.points.rows(), quad.points.cols()) * 0.5;
4728
4729 assert(fabs(quad.weights.sum() - 1) < 1e-14);
4730 assert(quad.points.minCoeff() >= 0 && quad.points.maxCoeff() <= 1);
4731
4732 assert((quad.points.size() == quad.weights.size()));
4733 quad.weights /= quad.weights.sum();
4734 }
